citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at approximately
3:00pm on 16-JAN-2024.
Inspector went to the address provided in the customer's application for registration and was told the registrant did not live
at this address. The number provided by the customer in his application for registration was then called and the response
communicated that the phone number dialed was no longer in service.
End Section

Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
